---
// Shipping container delivery policy
---

<section class="bg-background text-foreground">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-12">
    <p class="text-base text-muted-foreground mb-8">IronBox Containers delivers shipping containers nationwide. This policy outlines our shipping timeframes, costs, delivery requirements, and what to expect when your container arrives.</p>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-base text-muted-foreground">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Delivery Timeframe</h2>
        <p><strong class="text-foreground">Standard Delivery:</strong> 5-10 business days nationwide</p>
        <ul class="mt-2 ml-6 space-y-1 list-disc">
          <li><strong>Order Processing:</strong> 1-2 business days to prepare your container for shipment</li>
          <li><strong>Transit Time:</strong> 4-8 business days depending on your location</li>
          <li><strong>Total Delivery:</strong> 5-10 business days from order confirmation</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">Delivery times may vary based on your location, weather conditions, and carrier schedules. We will provide tracking information once your container ships.</p>
        <p class="mt-2"><strong>Custom Containers:</strong> Modified or customized containers require additional fabrication time (typically 2-6 weeks) before shipping.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Shipping Costs</h2>
        <p><strong class="text-foreground">Flat Rate Nationwide Shipping: $300</strong></p>
        <p class="mt-2">We offer simple, affordable flat rate shipping of just $300 to anywhere in South Africa, regardless of distance.</p>

        <p class="mt-3"><strong>What's Included:</strong></p>
        <ul class="mt-2 ml-6 space-y-1 list-disc">
          <li>Nationwide delivery to any location in South Africa</li>
          <li>Standard tilt-bed truck delivery</li>
          <li>Professional driver and delivery coordination</li>
          <li>All applicable permits and transportation fees</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="mt-3"><strong>Additional Services (Optional):</strong></p>
        <ul class="mt-2 ml-6 space-y-1 list-disc">
          <li><strong>Crane Delivery:</strong> Contact us for a quote if you need crane placement</li>
          <li><strong>Forklift Delivery:</strong> Available for tight spaces (additional fees may apply)</li>
          <li><strong>Expedited Delivery:</strong> Rush delivery available upon request</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="mt-2">Shipping costs are calculated at checkout and are non-refundable once your order is processed.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Delivery Requirements</h2>
        <p>To ensure successful delivery, your site must meet the following requirements:</p>

        <p class="mt-3 font-semibold text-foreground">Site Access:</p>
        <ul class="mt-2 ml-6 space-y-1 list-disc">
          <li>Clear, straight-line access for a tilt-bed delivery truck (minimum 14 feet wide)</li>
          <li>Overhead clearance of at least 14 feet</li>
          <li>Firm, level ground capable of supporting a loaded delivery truck (18,000+ kg)</li>
          <li>No low-hanging power lines, tree branches, or obstructions</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="mt-3 font-semibold text-foreground">Placement Surface:</p>
        <ul class="mt-2 ml-6 space-y-1 list-disc">
          <li>Level, compacted surface (gravel, concrete, asphalt, or compacted earth)</li>
          <li>Adequate drainage to prevent water pooling under the container</li>
          <li>Foundation blocks, piers, or concrete pads (recommended but not required)</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="mt-3 font-semibold text-foreground">Permits & Regulations:</p>
        <ul class="mt-2 ml-6 space-y-1 list-disc">
          <li>Customer is responsible for obtaining any required permits for container placement</li>
          <li>Verify local zoning regulations allow shipping containers on your property</li>
          <li>Check HOA restrictions if applicable</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="mt-2"><strong>Important:</strong> If the delivery truck cannot safely access your site or the ground is unsuitable, delivery may be refused or rescheduled at the customer's expense.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Delivery Process</h2>
        <p><strong>Before Delivery:</strong></p>
        <ul class="mt-2 ml-6 space-y-1 list-disc">
          <li>You will receive tracking information and estimated delivery window via email</li>
          <li>Our delivery team will contact you 24-48 hours in advance to schedule delivery</li>
          <li>Ensure your site meets all delivery requirements (see above)</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="mt-3"><strong>On Delivery Day:</strong></p>
        <ul class="mt-2 ml-6 space-y-1 list-disc">
          <li>Someone must be present to accept delivery and sign for the container</li>
          <li>Deliveries typically occur Monday-Saturday between 7AM-5PM local time</li>
          <li>Driver will offload the container using a tilt-bed truck</li>
          <li>Inspect the container for damage before signing the delivery receipt</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="mt-3"><strong>After Delivery:</strong></p>
        <ul class="mt-2 ml-6 space-y-1 list-disc">
          <li>Report any shipping damage within 48 hours to support@ironboxcontainers.com</li>
          <li>Take photos of any damage for claims processing</li>
          <li>Review our Return & Refund Policy if the container is not as described</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Delivery Methods</h2>
        <p><strong>Standard Tilt-Bed Delivery (Included):</strong></p>
        <p class="mt-2">Most containers are delivered via tilt-bed truck, which tilts the bed and slides the container onto the ground. This method requires adequate space (approximately 40-60 feet) for the truck to maneuver.</p>

        <p class="mt-3"><strong>Crane Delivery (Additional Cost):</strong></p>
        <p class="mt-2">If your site has limited access or you need the container placed in a specific location, crane delivery is available at an additional cost. Contact us for a crane delivery quote.</p>

        <p class="mt-3"><strong>Forklift Delivery (Additional Cost):</strong></p>
        <p class="mt-2">For smaller containers (10ft, 20ft) in tight spaces, forklift delivery may be available. This service requires advance arrangement.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Delivery Delays & Issues</h2>
        <p><strong>Delays:</strong> Shipping delays may occur due to weather, carrier schedules, or unforeseen circumstances. We will notify you of any delays as soon as possible.</p>
        <p class="mt-2"><strong>Failed Delivery:</strong> If the driver cannot safely access your site or you are not present to accept delivery, a redelivery fee of $200-$500 may apply.</p>
        <p class="mt-2"><strong>Damage Claims:</strong> Report any shipping damage within 48 hours of delivery. Include photos and a detailed description. Approved claims will be resolved through repair, replacement, or refund.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Tracking Your Order</h2>
        <p>Once your container ships, you will receive:</p>
        <ul class="mt-2 ml-6 space-y-1 list-disc">
          <li>Shipping confirmation email with tracking information</li>
          <li>Carrier contact information</li>
          <li>Estimated delivery window</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">You can also track your order by logging into your account at <a href="/account" class="text-primary hover:underline">ironboxcontainers.com/account</a> or contacting customer support at +27 11 234 5678.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">International Shipping</h2>
        <p>At this time, we only ship within South Africa. We do not currently offer shipping to international destinations.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-8 border-t border-border mt-12">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-4">Contact Us</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-2">For any questions regarding shipping or delivery, please contact us:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-muted-foreground">
          <li><strong>IronBox Containers</strong></li>
          <li>15 Electron Avenue, Isando</li>
          <li>Kempton Park, Gauteng, 1600</li>
          <li>South Africa</li>
          <li>Email: <a href="mailto:support@ironboxcontainers.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">support@ironboxcontainers.com</a></li>
          <li>Phone: <a href="tel:+27112345678" class="text-primary hover:underline">+27 11 234 5678</a></li>
          <li>Business Hours: Mon-Fri: 8AM-6PM | Sat: 9AM-4PM (Central Time)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
